description:
Five Star Coin Pro (FSCP ) aims to provide user-friendly, efficient, and secure crypto banking, payments, and blockchain-based eCommerce solutions. Through machine-learning algorithms, coin proof of stake issuances, and FSCP holder proof of stakes, FSCP aims to become widely accepted as a medium of exchange and a store of value.
